{"tid":2096051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：港區國安法實施有很大震懾力　反中亂港分子已退縮","createTime":"2020-07-06T02:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T15:48:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e9b899f56839ccb52c608d5d0dec2d6c9a91b1","tid":2096051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:00:12.000Z","msg":"香港警務處長鄧炳強昨（5日）接受央視專訪時表示，警務處成立了新的國家安全處，將全力配合香港維護國家安全委員會的工作，將企圖分裂國家之人繩之於法。他稱，有充分證據顯示，《港區國安法》實施後已有很大的震懾力，一些「反中亂港」分子已開始退縮，《港區國安法》必將對社會穩定起到關鍵作用。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強亦說，國安法的實施為警隊打擊分裂國家等罪行的執法提供了法律依據，極大增強了警隊維護國家安全的信心。他稱過去一年香港發生很多暴力事件，部分行為涉及威脅國家安全，以往沒有法例規管相關行為，但《港區國安法》明確列出罪行，令警隊執法有法可依。"},{"pid":"915d2ad0f11de8482a8cbea6a3ed3774a9eb8913","tid":2096051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200706/s00001/1593998764458/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200706%2Fs00001%2F1593998764458%2F&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96Fv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=47751ae7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200706%2Fs00001%2F1593998764458%2F&h=143ae082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200706/s00001/1593998764458/</a>"},{"pid":"55b604e41031588dc126ebcb7186064358cfbe56","tid":2096051,"uid":104804,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"放棄BNO未"},{"pid":"2d4e11a55c8817878def748122497d3bf5281106","tid":2096051,"uid":11447,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:01:56.000Z","msg":"國家安全了 不需要香港警隊了"},{"pid":"dea1457951a2b277293d70aa8a445da7bcca72b6","tid":2096051,"uid":77453,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔係恐怖分子咩？ 國際級？"},{"pid":"b4a3123a9a0f207fea560e28801dbe3e825df548","tid":2096051,"uid":215876,